{"tid":378211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【天鴿襲澳】2長者被捕！涉WeChat謠傳政府暪停車場5死","createTime":"2017-08-28T10:13:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T14:34:03.000Z","uid":14918,"like":301,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"00add68e9660e384072151fb0258fefe8be63b7c","tid":378211,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:13:47.000Z","msg":"澳門司警扣留2名73歲和68歲的兄妹，他們涉嫌在網上發佈不實消息，包括聲稱政府封鎖在筷子基停車場發現5具遺體的消息。司警表示，有人未證實消息真確，就用手機通訊軟件「微信」（WeChat），轉載該不實消息到至少6個聊天群組、30個私人對話中。司警會以觸犯侵犯行使公共當局權力之法人罪，移送他們到檢察院。司警又表示，案件仍在調查，不排除有更多人涉案。"},{"pid":"94cd7a44b443e6e35144712a77c8a60c6feac796","tid":378211,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b44388e3c75325d749cf89524c862748b00ae7","tid":378211,"uid":36696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:14:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9a0c823ece3fae4dee23ccd00734110c153555","tid":378211,"uid":46910,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抵死"},{"pid":"2e60076ede70b31ad7911b43f9811fec4b32e543","tid":378211,"uid":70411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:14:59.000Z","msg":"2兄妹被捕"},{"pid":"8b2e63fd6ea666788e12d28ecc97f778e6999098","tid":378211,"uid":54481,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:15:05.000Z","msg":"23條"},{"pid":"335edcc5f20a089657959ab53e5d250bb13c3320","tid":378211,"uid":4304,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:15:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37132eb0f0e7d56a319a964dd843bf49da6d8761","tid":378211,"uid":14918,"l